title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-21-2013 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-21-2013 WED








The Glenn Beck Program - 08/21/13 






The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,




Glenn and the guys talk with Kirk Cameron about his latest movie, Unstoppable.

 Also, Glenn asks where is the outrage in America and our people worse now than in the past?

 Plus, the guys discuss violent video games and personal responsibility.
